data.description: Your opportunity at highly desirable Druid Forest - beautiful condo upper unit with upgrades galore!  Open Floorplan features Kitchen with Quartz Countertops, LG Stainless/Grey Appliance suite, LVP Floors, Custom distress treated Cabinets. Brand New Washer & Dryer with Pedestals as well! Living Room with welcoming Gas Fireplace, sliding glass door to your own Private Balcony retreat for morning coffee. Two large Bedrooms and two full bathrooms add convenience. Walk-in Closet in Main Bedroom. This condominium has been rejuvenated top to bottom with new water heater, HVAC, Appliances - - ready to be your next home! Unbeatable Druid Hills location just minutes from Buckhead, Brookhaven and Midtown, and steps away from Emory, restaurants, shopping, entertainment. Well-run HOA. Yes there are rental restrictions. VA-approved.
